title: build(deps-dev): bump codelyzer from 5.1.2 to 5.2.0

body:
Bumps [codelyzer](https://github.com/mgechev/codelyzer) from 5.1.2 to 5.2.0.
Changelog *Sourced from [codelyzer's changelog](https://github.com/mgechev/codelyzer/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md).* > ## [5.2.0](https://github.com/mgechev/codelyzer/compare/5.1.2...5.2.0) (2019-10-22) > > ### Bug Fixes > > - **deps:** update angular monorepo ([#867](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mgechev/codelyzer/issues/867)) ([98ff423](https://github.com/mgechev/codelyzer/commit/98ff423)) > - **deps:** update dependency codelyzer to v5.1.2 ([#900](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mgechev/codelyzer/issues/900)) ([9b0caec](https://github.com/mgechev/codelyzer/commit/9b0caec)) > > ### Features > > - support typescript 3.6 ([#915](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/mgechev/codelyzer/issues/915)) ([dcb0218](https://github.com/mgechev/codelyzer/commit/dcb0218))
Commits - See full diff in [compare view](https://github.com/mgechev/codelyzer/commits)
